{"tid":779204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用三叔既都係傻仔","createTime":"2018-08-14T08:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T11:13:49.000Z","uid":59536,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8fe35d2213a66bc6c4df1bb1bb1ed4a4716f88","tid":779204,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n返工成日有個著格仔衫既毒撚 佢好鐘意用三叔 成日話三叔手機世界第一<br />\n係公司既IT 成日我都叫佢 搬下水 換下燈咁  <br />\n雖然樣好多過班金鐘仔少少  不過都係無前途<br />\n<br />\n靚靚女同事成日都著黑絲短裙 好正既 最近係港大畢業 之前好似住咩 STAR hall  好純既好乖既 仲未有男朋友  我成日想約佢食飯 佢都話要陪屋企人 真係好考順<br />\n最近聽佢講想買部電話 話備用既sony 機 成日都好熱. <br />\n我之後買左部iphone X 係佢生日既時候俾佢 話想做佢男朋友 不過佢都拒絕左 <br />\n話想暫時專注係事業上 第日有機會會考慮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日係茶水間唔小心聽到佢公司既靚靚女同事講野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 毒撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 靚靚女同事<br />\n<br />\n毒撚 : 你放工上唔上我屋企睇我note 9  好長嫁有成6.4吋 <br />\n<br />\n女同事 : 6.4吋姐係幾長啊 <br />\n<br />\n毒撚 : 長過Iphone X  少少囉 . <br />\n<br />\n聽到呢到 我就諗緊個死毒撚一定想女同事轉會 用三叔機 <br />\n<br />\n我靈機一觸 就攞出我部iphone X 開埋個錄音機<br />\n<br />\n毒撚 :我 note 9 仲要好持久 包你滿意 <br />\n<br />\n女同事 : 吓 真係嫁? 不過唔會上你屋企啵 <br />\n<br />\n之後我就無聽了 好似仲話唔知今晚去百佳睇<br />\n<br />\n毒撚出黎既時候仲口噏噏 話成一皮約一次 真係正 <br />\n<br />\n我心諗死毒撚 連餐廳都唔識約 一世都溝唔囡<br />\n<br />\n我宜家就draft 緊e mail 連埋錄音 SEND 俾 HR 話隻IT 狗性騷擾女同事<br />\n<br />\n聽日等睇佢 俾人炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe53e5aca0e896f410c2bc75b5faf7686a78612d","tid":779204,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"105e5ba268892735cafb0a3c162411f24857400a","tid":779204,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe53e5aca0e896f410c2bc75b5faf7686a78612d","tid":779204,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"10/10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64ef394652b6c703079a4190ee4d5de30dc8944","tid":779204,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"你女同事係雞黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e5365720f87589e23b3e5acce19f4a972627c8","tid":779204,"uid":32485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e64ef394652b6c703079a4190ee4d5de30dc8944","tid":779204,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"你女同事係雞黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"唔記得轉ACCOUNT? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddef0016f4f14c5acd25551a54ac5a95e343810","tid":779204,"uid":23468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92e5365720f87589e23b3e5acce19f4a972627c8","tid":779204,"uid":32485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e64ef394652b6c703079a4190ee4d5de30dc8944","tid":779204,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"你女同事係雞黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"唔記得轉ACCOUNT? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2